        <mxCell id="cp_t0" value="T0 — Routine&#10;skip steps 2 (analysts), 4 (debate), 7 (LLM risk team), 9 (fund manager LLM check). Just trader + rule-based preflight." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Calibri;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="cond_panel">
